{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Thrilling battles</h2>Wandering Desert Island features powerful bosses, dangerous dungeons, and monsters spawning in different island biomes.<br>You can match weapons and equipment to unlock powerful skills to slash, block, tumble and destroy these monsters to survive!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/\u780d\u6740\u52a8\u56fe.gif?t=1719341682\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Classic sandbox survival gameplay</h2>Farming and fishing, cutting down trees and digging for mines, building huts, these are all indispensable.<br>However, you don't need pickaxes and axes to sabotage here, an iron sword is enough.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/\u517b\u8001\u52a8\u56fe.gif?t=1719341682\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unlock and grow technology</h2>Technology changes lives, and with these technologies, you can upgrade your home. Expanded lighting, rapid watering, resource regeneration...<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/\u79d1\u6280\u52a8\u56fe.gif?t=1719341682\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore the island and visit NPCs</h2>Not all islands are deserted, and some are inhabited by residents! Deal with the residents and trade goods with them.<br>Each island has unique creatures and resources to explore.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/\u63a2\u7d22\u52a8\u56fe.gif?t=1719341682\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1719341682","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1719341682","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/capsule_231x87.